title: BimlFlex Settings Definition for EnableEndDatePsa
description: Apply end dating in the PSA. This will allow timelines to be maintained in the PSA. Using end dating requires more resources since updates are applied on the PSA, but allows queries to directly reuse complete effective from and to dates for each record in the PSA. Disable this to configure an insert-only approach for the PSA for optimized load performance.
